name: CREAM
description:
Creamies is a brand that descibes itself as the bridge between DeFi, NFTs, and degen games.

Starting with their collection of 1,111 Korean inspired ‘emoticon NFTs’, they have also minted 111 Master Creamers NFTs, and most recently their 'Creamlands' collection. 

CREAM is the native token of the Creamies ecosystem.
